138
00:13:35,180 --> 00:13:38,059
First, may Grandfather have a long life.

139
00:13:38,060 --> 00:13:41,120
(First, may Grandfather
live a long life.)

140
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:46,279
Second, may Minghui
prosper forever.

141
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:49,040
(Second, may Minghui)

142
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:54,600
(prosper forever.)

143
00:13:56,660 --> 00:13:57,739
Third, may Shen Gu

144
00:13:57,740 --> 00:13:59,400
(Third, may)

145
00:14:03,460 --> 00:14:04,900
