162
00:16:26,640 --> 00:16:31,960
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

163
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:38,920
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

164
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:46,280
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

165
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:52,080
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

166
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:59,119
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

167
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:01,999
♪The promise we made♪

168
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:05,679
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

169
00:17:05,680 --> 00:17:12,279
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

170
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:18,680
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

171
00:17:19,080 --> 00:17:25,399
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

172
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:30,520
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

173
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:34,000
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
